    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Shutdown Xenothreat Comm Towers",
    "Description": "Citizens for Prosperity are eager to help the people of Pyro, and it starts with freeing them from the grasp of XenoThreat.\n\nWe\u2019re preparing a team to infiltrate one of their outposts, but we need someone to go in ahead to take out their communication towers first. Once those towers are offline, they won\u2019t be able to call for reinforcements and we can proceed with our plan.\n\nHead to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and find the towers. At the <EM4>top is a control panel</EM4> that can be used to disable them.\n\nAlso, it\u2019s worth noting that most outposts use a similar system, so you\u2019ll know how to disable the comms towers rather than risk fighting reinforcement dropships when you\u2019re doing other jobs.\n\nGood luck,\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
